name: Boushh
Lore: 'Leia obtained the armor of a notorious mercenary to sneak onto Coruscant. She later assumed the same role to spy on Jabba. Fearless and inventive. Jabba''s kind of scum.',
Text: 'Deploys only to a site (-2 on Tatooine or Coruscant) as an Undercover Spy. While undercover at an opponents site, prevents opponent from modifying or cancelling your Force Drains at opponent''s related sites. Immune to Attrition < 3.',
